<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/app.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

    <div class="home-backround1">
        <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
            <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
              <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
                <img src="images/home_page_image.jpg" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid home-image" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">This Blog For Everyone</h1>
                <p class="lead my-5">There is an article for everyone here. It is possible to write a post without being a user and logging in, just by entering your name information. What is important is not identity, but thoughts...</p>
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start my-5">
                  <a href="/write"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">Write Something...</button></a>
                 <a href="/posts"><button  type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">See Others Posts</button></a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr-style">
   
    <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
        <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="images/home_page_blog_icon.png" alt="" height="100px">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">You Can Find Anything</h1>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
            <p class="lead mb-4">You can go to the 'Posts' section to see all the content. You can also share your own content from the 'Write something' section above. You can write your own ideas freely and do so anonymously by simply entering your name.<br><br>If you want to search by topic, you can select the chapters you want to read by searching in the 'Search' section.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr-style">

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
   
</body>
</html>